data.chText: 满是肥皂的；涂满肥皂的
data.enText: full of soap; covered with soap

data.chText: 有肥皂味的；摸着像肥皂的

tr: unpleasantly and excessively suave or ingratiating in manner or speech
resembling or having the qualities of soap

value.def: Something that is soapy is full of soap or covered with soap.

example.ex: Wash your hands thoroughly with hot soapy water before handling any food.
example.tran: 在拿吃的之前，用热肥皂水把手好好地洗干净。

value.tran: 满是肥皂泡的;涂满肥皂的
